<doc id="1183387" wikidata="Q19748849" url="?curid=1183387" title="Tarombo">
<text>Tarombo is a term for genealogy in Batak culture/language. The Batak believe that they all come from the same ancestor: Si Raja Batak, the Batak patriarch. They kept the genealogy line tracing back to this ancestor, called Tarombo Batak. Its origins have been clouded with legends.

