<doc id="1183466" wikidata="Q491428" url="?curid=1183466" title="Park Sang-min (actor)">
<text>Park Sang-min (born October 9, 1970) is a South Korean actor. He is best known for Im Kwon-taek&#x27;s &quot;General&#x27;s Son&quot; trilogy and his roles in numerous television dramas such as &quot;My Lovely Fool&quot; and &quot;Giant&quot;.

Park has had run-ins with the law: a drunk driving arrest in 2011, and a domestic violence charge in 2012.

